cpansec-feed (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Redesign validation report: one row per vulnerability, sorted newest first.
  * Add Published and Updated date columns with relative time display.
  * Make Distribution and date columns sortable.
  * Add clickable links for CVE records (cve.org) and CPANSA files (GitHub).
  * Stop merging CPANSA data into CPANSec authoritative CVE records.
  * Deduplicate CPANSA source advisories and report rows.
  * Distinguish CPANSec CVE, CPANSA (external CNA), and CPANSA-only statuses.
  * Rename report title to CPANSec Feed.

